In tu'azzibhum fa innahum'iba-duk(a), wa in tagfir lahum fa innaka antal 'azizul hakim(u).
Qa-lalla-hu ha-za- yaumu yanfa'us sa-diqina sidquhum, lahum janna-tun tajri min tahtihal anha-ru kha-lidina fiha- abada-(n), radiyalla-hu'anhum wa radu- 'anh(u), za-likal fauzul 'azim(u).
Lilla-hi mulkus sama-wa-ti wal ardi wa ma- fihinn(a), wa huwa 'ala- kulli syai'in qadir(un).
